title: Clavicular and Jenny Popach clash on live stream as girlfriend Violet’s anger sparks shocking viral controversy
summary_full: A viral Kick stream showed Clavicular’s girlfriend Violet fighting with TikTok star Jenny Popach after a heated argument. The issue began when Violet believed Jenny was flirting with Clavicular on camera. The moment spread fast on X. Clavicular later said he did not understand how the fight even started.
